CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1776280294
OL,3,CGuernsey decline DFDS inter-island
OL,4,Cservice
OL,6,FGuernsey's Economic Development
OL,7,FCommittee has rejected proposals from
OL,8,FJersey's ferry provider, DFDS, to run
OL,9,Fa service between the two islands.
OL,11,FThe proposition would have seen the
OL,12,FStena Vinga ship arrive in Guernsey
OL,13,Flate on a Friday evening and return to
OL,14,FJersey late on a Monday afternoon.
OL,16,FThe Committee say they assessed the
OL,17,Fplans alongside Guernsey Ports and
OL,18,FCustoms and Immigration.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1776280294
OL,3,CGuernsey decline DFDS inter-island
OL,4,Cservice
OL,6,FThey considered the impact on existing
OL,7,Fferry operations, Guernsey's port
OL,8,Finfrastructure, and political context
OL,9,F- including Jersey's promise to
OL,10,Fdeliver a reciprocal inter-island
OL,11,Fservice once a week after signing a 20-
OL,12,Fyear contract with DFDS.
OL,14,FIn a statement, the Committee say the
OL,15,Fproposed schedule "presents material
OL,16,Foperational and resourcing challenges
OL,17,Fto Guernsey Ports and Customs and
OL,18,FImmigration", with the Friday evening
OL,19,Farrival falling outside the port's
OL,20,Fstandard operating hours.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1776280294
OL,3,CGuernsey decline DFDS inter-island
OL,4,Cservice
OL,6,FThe Committee also raises concerns
OL,7,Fabout the "deliverability of the
OL,8,Fproposed service and the availability
OL,9,Fof Stena Vinga, given the public
OL,10,Freports that it would require
OL,11,Fmaintenance."
OL,13,FThey conclude: "The proposal, as
OL,14,Fsubmitted, does not align with the
OL,15,Fprinciples of reciprocity that have
OL,16,Fpreviously been articulated by both
OL,17,Fgovernments as the basis for
OL,18,Fstrengthening inter-island links."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1776280294
OL,3,CGuernsey decline DFDS inter-island
OL,4,Cservice
OL,6,FThe Committee's President, Deputy
OL,7,FSasha Kazantseva-Miller, adds: "We
OL,8,Frecognise the importance of strong and
OL,9,Freliable inter-island connectivity,
OL,10,Fparticularly at weekends, and we
OL,11,Fremain committed to improvements that
OL,12,Fgenuinely benefit the Bailiwick as a
OL,13,Fwhole.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1776280294
OL,3,CGuernsey decline DFDS inter-island
OL,4,Cservice
OL,6,F"We remain very open to further
OL,7,Fdiscussions on potential solutions
OL,8,Fthat are operationally viable, legally
OL,9,Frobust, and capable of delivering a
OL,10,Fgenuinely reciprocal service,
OL,11,Fcomparable to the high-speed return
OL,12,Fmodel currently offered by Brittany
OL,13,FFerries."
OL,15,FShe adds the Committee will work
OL,16,Falongside both DFDS and the States of
OL,17,FJersey to find ways to "enhance inter-
OL,18,Fisland connectivity" whilst ensuring
OL,19,F"fairness, sustainability, and
OL,20,Fconsistency with Guernsey's
OL,21,Foperational requirements".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
