OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1776280294
OL,3,CGuernsey decline DFDS inter-island
OL,4,Cservice
OL,6,FGuernsey's chosen ferry provider -
OL,7,FBrittany Ferries - currently offers a
OL,8,Fonce-weekly inter-island service.
OL,10,FITV News has contacted DFDS for
OL,11,Fcomment.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/6
